      <h1>Ownership — leasehold transfer</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        When the ownership being transferred is leasehold, this cluster
        is the assignment of the lease — its term, the people who own and
        manage it, ground rent, service charge, consents, and assorted
        legal artefacts. Eight sub-pages each scope one part of the
        leasehold disclosure.
      </p>
      <h2 id="subpages">Pages in this cluster</h2>
      <ul class="cluster-index">
        <li><a href="38e1-lease-term.html"><strong>Term &amp; shared ownership</strong></a> — lease term, shared-ownership percentage and rent schedule.</li>
        <li><a href="38e2-lease-contacts-list.html"><strong>Contact list</strong></a> — freeholder, management company, agent, sinking-fund holder.</li>
        <li><a href="38e3-lease-contacts-roles.html"><strong>Service-contact roles</strong></a> — which contact does what.</li>
        <li><a href="38e4-lease-management.html"><strong>Management</strong></a> — ownership-and-management structure and obligations.</li>
        <li><a href="38e5-lease-rent.html"><strong>Ground rent</strong></a> — schedule, escalation, payment terms.</li>
        <li><a href="38e6-lease-charges.html"><strong>Service charge &amp; insurance</strong></a> — service-charge accounts, buildings insurance schedule.</li>
        <li><a href="38e7-lease-legal.html"><strong>Consents, restrictions, alterations, safety</strong></a> — landlord consents, lease restrictions, alterations, enfranchisement, Building Safety Act.</li>
        <li><a href="38e8-lease-misc.html"><strong>Disputes, general, documents, confirmation</strong></a> — disputes, general declarations, required documents, accuracy confirmation.</li>
      </ul>
      <PageFooter
  prev={{ href: '38d-ownership-freehold.html', label: 'Ownership — freehold' }}
